Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.02,0:00:07.98,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to run in the Hakone Ekiden.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.37,0:00:10.70,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Starting today, I'm going\Nto win over all the guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.07,0:00:15.35,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,That includes you,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.78,0:00:17.78,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Sendai Josei High School graduate,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.78,0:00:19.18,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Kurahara Kakeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.26,0:00:29.80,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,Just who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.69,0:00:36.14,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,There, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.14,0:00:37.59,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,You must be hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.98,0:00:40.10,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Let's head back. Time for breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.15,0:02:18.99,Series_Title,SHOW,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1)}Run with the Wind
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.36,0:02:21.32,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,We can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.22,0:02:23.33,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,Not Hakone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.02,0:02:25.37,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.14,0:02:29.79,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,No one knows that for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.56,0:02:31.83,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.50,0:02:38.45,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,The top track and field teams\Ntrain every day for years,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.45,0:02:42.06,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,but only a handful of them even qualify.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.85,0:02:44.60,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,That's the kind of race it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.93,0:02:48.32,main,BLUE,0000,0000,0000,,You know a lot about Hakone Ekiden?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.21,0:02:51.69,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.02,0:02:54.50,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Dreams do come true if you try.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.44,0:02:58.86,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Nico-chan Senpai has \Ntrack and field experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.19,0:02:59.99,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.35,0:03:02.87,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki made it to a prefectural\Nkendo tournament with his team.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.57,0:03:07.28,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,The twins and King played soccer\Nfor three years in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.14,0:03:13.38,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Shindo used to walk ten kilometers through\Nthe mountains to get to school and back everyday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.75,0:03:16.24,main,KING,0000,0000,0000,,That's not a sport.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.24,0:03:19.09,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,And Musa has a hidden talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.09,0:03:23.34,main,MUSA,0000,0000,0000,,It's prejudiced to think \Nblack people are fast runners.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.83,0:03:27.13,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,I confirmed in the bath\N that you've got good muscles.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.13,0:03:29.11,main,MUSA,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you're always staring at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.11,0:03:30.74,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Then there's Kurahara.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.33,0:03:34.52,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,I want you guys to see how he runs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.88,0:03:40.25,main,PRINCE,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, but I wasn't included just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.72,0:03:42.22,main,PRINCE,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, I don't have to run—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.22,0:03:44.24,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,We finally have ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.51,0:03:47.06,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, you're included.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.38,0:04:13.27,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to run with you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.65,0:04:21.57,Ep_title,EPTITLE,0000,0000,0000,,The Ogre's Arrival
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.98,0:04:44.93,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Kurahara, there's an open seat there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.93,0:04:45.70,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.64,0:04:51.68,main,SHINDO,0000,0000,0000,,Latecomers sit over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.01,0:04:54.36,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Have as many helpings as you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.70,0:04:57.32,main,MUSA,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.32,0:05:00.28,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.28,0:05:01.86,main,KING,0000,0000,0000,,That chair's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.86,0:05:05.65,Calendar_items(ep 02),TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Chikusei-so Cleaning Duty Schedule
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.17,0:05:08.30,main,MUSA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to clean the toilets.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.30,0:05:10.16,main,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.93,0:05:17.48,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to feed Nira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.50,0:05:31.31,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,No one's going along with Haiji's plan, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.59,0:05:35.65,main,NICO,0000,0000,0000,,That thing he mentioned yesterday? Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.65,0:05:37.85,main,KING,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way. Absolutely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.85,0:05:40.61,main,PURPLE,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really? Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.61,0:05:45.07,main,BLUE,0000,0000,0000,,I was going to run away\Nif you guys said you'd do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.28,0:05:47.78,main,SHINDO,0000,0000,0000,,It's too sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.09,0:05:49.83,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,It's a scam.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.83,0:05:51.74,main,NICO,0000,0000,0000,,What did Musa say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.22,0:05:54.82,main,SHINDO,0000,0000,0000,,Between school and work, he's too busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.82,0:05:57.07,main,KING,0000,0000,0000,,So everyone's against it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.07,0:05:58.72,main,KING,0000,0000,0000,,Got it, newbie?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.28,0:06:02.11,main,PRINCE,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.79,0:06:05.59,main,PRINCE,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt he'd just back down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.31,0:06:10.59,main,PRINCE,0000,0000,0000,,These are the most luxurious dishes\Nwe've been served all month.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.55,0:06:16.05,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,He's domesticated us, hasn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.13,0:06:22.00,main,BLUE,0000,0000,0000,,I know, Kakeru. We're going to school today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.00,0:06:22.85,main,BLUE,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.85,0:06:23.57,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.57,0:06:26.75,main,PURPLE,0000,0000,0000,,We thought we'd check things out\Nbefore the entrance ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.28,0:06:30.24,Kansei_University_06:27(Ep 02),SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Kansei University
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.71,0:06:36.55,main,BLUE,0000,0000,0000,,Joji, they've got a soccer club.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.07,0:06:40.44,main,PURPLE,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, there's about five.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.44,0:06:42.67,main,PURPLE,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know which to join.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.46,0:06:45.50,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to keep playing soccer?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.81,0:06:46.67,main,BLUE,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.67,0:06:50.35,main,BLUE,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you heard what Haiji said.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.35,0:06:52.58,main,PURPLE,0000,0000,0000,,That makes it harder to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.03,0:06:55.72,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares if you want to play soccer?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.72,0:06:58.18,main,BLUE,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that we want to play soccer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.49,0:07:00.64,main,PURPLE,0000,0000,0000,,The problem is the girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.64,0:07:01.34,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.34,0:07:03.43,main,PURPLE,0000,0000,0000,,Who doesn't love a cute manager?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.43,0:07:05.87,main,BLUE,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, the futsal team is co-ed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.87,0:07:07.61,main,PURPLE,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously? Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.61,0:07:10.57,Comics_Club_07:07(Ep 02),SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Manga Club
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.93,0:07:10.12,main,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,We are the manga club.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.57,0:07:12.24,main,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,We hope you'll consider joining us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.53,0:07:15.42,main,PRINCE,0000,0000,0000,,We're accepting new members.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.77,0:07:17.93,main,PRINCE,0000,0000,0000,,Want to join the club?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.93,0:07:19.58,main,PRINCE,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, write your name—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.11,0:07:23.54,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,You seem energetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.77,0:07:27.42,main,PRINCE,0000,0000,0000,,Could you not stand there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.42,0:07:33.68,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,It won't be easy for you to pack,\Nso I thought I'd tell you first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.20,0:07:35.22,main,PRINCE,0000,0000,0000,,Pack?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.61,0:07:41.85,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, you can't stay at Aotake\Nif you're not on the track and field team.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.85,0:07:46.93,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, if you refuse \Nto be on the team, you have to move—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.93,0:07:48.23,main,PRINCE,0000,0000,0000,,You're kicking me out?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.23,0:07:51.24,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,No, no. Careful how you phrase it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.24,0:07:54.13,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just saying you can't\Nlive there if you don't ru—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.13,0:07:56.01,main,PRINCE,0000,0000,0000,,You're kicking me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.01,0:07:57.31,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you could say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.94,0:08:02.08,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,It'll cost a fortune to move all that stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.08,0:08:06.03,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,But you don't have to leave\Nif you join the team.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.71,0:08:08.67,Placement_Office_08:06(Ep 02),SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Placement Office
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.67,0:08:13.13,Placement_Office_poster(ep 02),TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Take a Job Fitness Exam
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.92,0:08:13.13,Placement_Office_poster(ep 02),TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Eligible subjects
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.59,0:08:13.13,Placement_Office_poster(ep 02),TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,University students
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.34,0:08:13.13,Placement_Office_poster(ep 02),TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Details
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.09,0:08:13.13,Placement_Office_poster(ep 02),TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Use your computer to:
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.59,0:08:13.13,Placement_Office_poster(ep 02),TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,1) Receive an evaluation 3) Find the right job
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.97,0:08:13.13,Placement_Office_poster(ep 02),TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,2) Search for job information 4) Plan your career
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.59,0:08:13.13,Placement_Office_poster(ep 02),TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,You'll get to experience all four steps in choosing a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.43,0:08:17.14,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Looking for a job, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.90,0:08:23.13,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of a job do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.46,0:08:25.73,main,KING,0000,0000,0000,,Why should I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.73,0:08:27.88,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Mass media, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.88,0:08:29.49,main,KING,0000,0000,0000,,You already know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.00,0:08:33.78,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you could talk about\Nthe Ekiden at interviews.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.76,0:08:37.09,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,It's not something everyone gets to experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.09,0:08:37.99,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,It'll help.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.83,0:08:53.03,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,There wasn't a Mountain God this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.59,0:08:53.42,Final_summary_08:50(ep 02),TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1149,10)}University Ekiden Final Summary
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.93,0:08:56.36,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Well, they can't name one every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.36,0:08:57.89,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,It'd reduce its value.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.20,0:09:02.38,main,SHINDO,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Haiji. This is the library.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.38,0:09:03.40,main,SHINDO,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.40,0:09:04.84,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Shindo, how about where you're from?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.46,0:09:06.23,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Your hometown.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.75,0:09:08.83,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty mountainous, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.83,0:09:11.26,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,What's more treacherous? That or Hakone?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.26,0:09:13.49,main,SHINDO,0000,0000,0000,,I've never compared them...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.49,0:09:15.21,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't been home recently, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.62,0:09:17.57,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,You ever call home?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.57,0:09:19.66,main,SHINDO,0000,0000,0000,,Haiji, keep it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.97,0:09:24.46,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure your family \Nwould be delighted if they saw
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.46,0:09:27.71,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,the son they rarely see\Nenergetically running on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.61,0:09:32.14,main,SHINDO,0000,0000,0000,,It's time. I gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.14,0:09:33.87,main,SHINDO,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.17,0:09:38.47,Chikusei_so_09:35(Ep 02),SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Chikusei-so
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.93,0:09:46.85,102_09:40(Ep 02),SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,102
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.85,0:09:50.61,104_09:40(Ep 02),SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,104
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.23,0:09:53.67,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Nico-chan Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.40,0:10:05.37,main,NICO,0000,0000,0000,,You robbing me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.69,0:10:07.58,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.19,0:10:09.64,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Your cigarettes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.64,0:10:10.47,main,NICO,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.47,0:10:13.09,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't smell them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.09,0:10:15.55,main,NICO,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's because I was out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.55,0:10:16.51,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.29,0:10:18.29,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.31,0:10:20.68,main,NICO,0000,0000,0000,,Going to the club again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.97,0:10:23.49,main,NICO,0000,0000,0000,,Lawyers sure have got it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.49,0:10:26.56,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,You should hurry up and graduate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.81,0:10:55.16,main,NICO,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.25,0:11:06.68,main,GIRL,0000,0000,0000,,You should definitely join us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.26,0:11:06.68,Soccer_Club_11:04(Ep 02),SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Soccer Club
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.21,0:11:06.68,main,BLUE,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds really fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.96,0:11:07.75,main,GIRL,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.75,0:11:08.54,main,BLUE,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll join.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.54,0:11:09.18,main,PURPLE,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.02,0:11:12.89,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Think you'll enjoy your student life?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.43,0:11:16.78,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,If you're looking for a special-event\Nclub, I can introduce you to one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.30,0:11:21.24,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,It's an option if you're looking\Nto experience college life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.86,0:11:24.87,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,You sure? You could run.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.60,0:11:27.53,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,No one will criticize you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.46,0:11:40.67,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,If I want to run, I'll run alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.94,0:11:58.90,Chikusei_so_11:56(Ep 02),SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Chikusei-so
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.62,0:11:58.35,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.07,0:12:01.40,main,MUSA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.78,0:12:03.97,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you running?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.97,0:12:08.54,main,MUSA,0000,0000,0000,,I went to work early after dropping in\Non the new student symposium...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.03,0:12:08.54,Kobori_Butcher_Shop_12:06Ep 02),SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Kobori Butcher Shop
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.54,0:12:11.00,main,WOMAN,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for buying so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.00,0:12:14.09,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,No, thank you for accommodating me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.09,0:12:16.21,main,WOMAN,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.48,0:12:18.91,main,WOMAN,0000,0000,0000,,Musa always works so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.91,0:12:23.19,main,WOMAN,0000,0000,0000,,And you're a regular. We really appreciate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.19,0:12:24.98,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not that special.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.98,0:12:29.00,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I'm glad I introduced him to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.68,0:12:32.25,main,WOMAN,0000,0000,0000,,He's such a hard worker.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.25,0:12:35.15,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Heard that? Way to go, Musa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.15,0:12:37.07,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,She's complimenting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.07,0:12:40.61,main,MUSA,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.61,0:12:43.60,main,WOMAN,0000,0000,0000,,You've got a great friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.60,0:12:46.03,main,WOMAN,0000,0000,0000,,You should be grateful you met him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.03,0:12:47.50,main,WOMAN,0000,0000,0000,,That's a friend for life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.50,0:12:50.62,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Hear that, Musa? We're friends for life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.62,0:12:52.04,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Musa... Musa...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.71,0:12:56.46,main,MUSA,0000,0000,0000,,He asked me what my plans\Nwere for tomorrow morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.46,0:12:58.40,main,MUSA,0000,0000,0000,,and I responded that I wasn't busy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.40,0:13:01.25,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,He knew you couldn't say no.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.25,0:13:04.72,main,KING,0000,0000,0000,,He's going after our weaknesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.20,0:13:07.93,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,What are your excuses?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.96,0:13:12.72,main,KING,0000,0000,0000,,He said it would help me find a job...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.72,0:13:15.64,main,SHINDO,0000,0000,0000,,It's good for my health... like weight loss?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.64,0:13:18.65,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,What's it really? What deals\Ndid you make with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.65,0:13:20.19,main,SHINDO,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't make a deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.19,0:13:22.60,main,SHINDO,0000,0000,0000,,I really have been gaining weight lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.60,0:13:26.53,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! I shouldn't have\Nlet you go off on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.56,0:13:30.41,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Well, at least you're better than these two.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.41,0:13:33.25,main,PURPLE,0000,0000,0000,,It's not fair. Right, Jota?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.25,0:13:38.63,main,BLUE,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. We thought everyone \Nhad promised to run in the Ekiden.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.02,0:13:42.84,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Did you listen until \NHaiji was finished talking?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.84,0:13:46.19,main,PURPLE,0000,0000,0000,,He said everyone was running.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.91,0:13:48.80,main,BLUE,0000,0000,0000,,So we said we would, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.80,0:13:52.81,main,KING,0000,0000,0000,,You're getting mites everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.15,0:13:56.21,main,BLUE,0000,0000,0000,,But we thought we'd give it a shot, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.21,0:13:58.61,main,PURPLE,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Did you guys know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.61,0:14:01.10,main,PURPLE,0000,0000,0000,,Girls love guys who run in the Ekiden!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.10,0:14:08.49,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,That's only true of a handful of top finishers!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.49,0:14:11.41,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way we'll even qualify!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.41,0:14:13.22,main,PURPLE,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.22,0:14:15.64,main,PURPLE,0000,0000,0000,,You mean we can't just sign up for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.64,0:14:17.85,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even feel like explaining it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.85,0:14:19.08,main,PURPLE,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.08,0:14:21.24,main,BLUE,0000,0000,0000,,He said girls would love us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.24,0:14:22.24,main,PURPLE,0000,0000,0000,,The girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.24,0:14:24.06,main,BLUE,0000,0000,0000,,No one told me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.03,0:14:25.59,main,MUSA,0000,0000,0000,,Are the others okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.87,0:14:27.51,main,SHINDO,0000,0000,0000,,Who's not here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.51,0:14:30.25,main,KING,0000,0000,0000,,Nico-chan, Prince, and the newbie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.55,0:14:33.51,103_14:30(Ep 02),SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,103
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.51,0:14:35.27,main,MUSA,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru, are you in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.27,0:14:36.18,main,MUSA,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.36,0:14:39.24,main,SHINDO,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he's not back yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.48,0:14:46.94,main,TAZAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it broke now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.81,0:14:54.12,main,PRINCE,0000,0000,0000,,It's a miracle... my heart... didn't stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.25,0:14:57.84,main,TAZAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but you can't use \Nour bathroom until it's fixed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.84,0:14:59.32,main,TAZAKI,0000,0000,0000,,There's the Tsuru-no-yu Bathhouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.32,0:15:01.53,main,TAZAKI,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have to go there for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.52,0:15:10.02,main,BOY,0000,0000,0000,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.63,0:15:19.10,flashback,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,You sure? You could run.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.10,0:15:21.27,flashback,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,No one will criticize you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.76,0:15:42.57,main,NICO,0000,0000,0000,,It's just for a change of pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.57,0:15:45.66,main,NICO,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell the guys at Aotake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.21,0:15:49.26,main,NICO,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't look like you're going back, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.14,0:15:52.52,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,Do you actually want to run?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.52,0:15:53.59,main,NICO,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.91,0:15:56.12,main,NICO,0000,0000,0000,,I said it's for a change of pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.12,0:15:59.52,main,NICO,0000,0000,0000,,They're pitch black. There's no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.52,0:16:01.47,main,NICO,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I'm not cut out for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.89,0:16:06.19,main,NICO,0000,0000,0000,,You know a lot about running, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.75,0:16:09.53,main,NICO,0000,0000,0000,,You ever seen a runner \Nas rough around the edges as me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.41,0:16:13.95,main,PURPLE,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.78,0:16:16.13,main,PURPLE,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.13,0:16:18.65,main,BLUE,0000,0000,0000,,The bath's broken!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.97,0:16:22.50,main,NICO,0000,0000,0000,,Come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.50,0:16:25.13,main,NICO,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take you someplace fun before you leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.13,0:16:27.59,Tsuru-no-yu_16:25(Ep 02),SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuru-no-yu
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.81,0:16:27.59,main,JO,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.89,0:16:32.26,main,JO,0000,0000,0000,,That feels great.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.26,0:16:34.22,main,JO,0000,0000,0000,,It's so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.09,0:16:36.72,main,PRINCE,0000,0000,0000,,Hell on earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.15,0:16:39.60,main,PRINCE,0000,0000,0000,,That's what we call this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.14,0:16:47.25,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,You don't often hang out with the newbie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.49,0:16:51.74,main,JO,0000,0000,0000,,Jota, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.74,0:16:53.21,main,JO,0000,0000,0000,,Cut that out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.45,0:16:59.12,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.55,0:17:02.08,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,You're all here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.32,0:17:07.66,main,PRINCE,0000,0000,0000,,An ogre has arrived in hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.27,0:17:14.57,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,What? The landlord's bath broke?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.57,0:17:16.29,main,SHINDO,0000,0000,0000,,Surely Haiji didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.71,0:17:18.97,main,KING,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say it. I don't want to think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.03,0:17:22.61,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Kurahara? Nice bathhouse, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.61,0:17:25.51,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone else thinks it's too hot, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.51,0:17:27.48,main,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,So do you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.48,0:17:30.10,main,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,You're never in for more than a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.10,0:17:31.77,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,You're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.77,0:17:32.69,main,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.83,0:17:36.54,main,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,Haiji, are these guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.54,0:17:38.99,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. They're the residents of Aotake.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.25,0:17:40.49,main,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.50,0:17:44.73,main,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,So you've finally got ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.73,0:17:45.68,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.59,0:17:49.66,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a resident.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.47,0:17:57.43,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,I met him after I left yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.43,0:17:59.13,main,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,He's new, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.13,0:18:00.09,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,I said I'm not—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.09,0:18:01.30,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have a contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.30,0:18:02.00,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.00,0:18:04.23,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,To see who can stay in the bath longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.23,0:18:05.10,main,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.66,0:18:09.60,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,The loser does whatever the winner says.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.04,0:18:14.23,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to accept his challenge, Kurahara.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.23,0:18:16.49,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,If you refuse, I'll assume you're running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.30,0:18:19.96,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to run, then run.\NI won't keep chasing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.41,0:18:22.47,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,After all, you're fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.93,0:18:24.84,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,...when you're running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.71,0:18:32.96,main,JO,0000,0000,0000,,It's been three minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.48,0:18:36.55,main,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't push yourselves too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.51,0:18:43.47,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,You heard him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.81,0:18:47.05,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,Feel free to get out first.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.43,0:18:50.15,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Haiji's tenacity is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.15,0:18:54.33,main,NICO,0000,0000,0000,,He's a fourth-year. It's his last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.33,0:18:56.40,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you getting so sentimental?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.07,0:18:59.74,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to run with him, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.98,0:19:02.82,main,JO,0000,0000,0000,,Four minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.14,0:19:07.70,main,NICO,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki, why don't we have our own contest?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.70,0:19:08.50,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.87,0:19:10.71,main,NICO,0000,0000,0000,,We'll bet on who wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.71,0:19:13.61,main,NICO,0000,0000,0000,,If you win, I'll do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.61,0:19:16.42,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,What? That's not fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.09,0:19:17.92,main,NICO,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.61,0:19:26.28,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,The newbie, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.67,0:19:29.20,main,NICO,0000,0000,0000,,Are you even trying to win?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.99,0:19:47.58,main,SHINDO,0000,0000,0000,,Water! Water, water!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.58,0:19:49.71,main,JO,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.71,0:19:51.21,main,JO,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you have to be so stubborn?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.21,0:19:53.30,main,KING,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad, newbie.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.72,0:19:57.94,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do in the case of a tie?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.24,0:20:09.83,main,NICO,0000,0000,0000,,That was disgraceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.69,0:20:15.72,main,NICO,0000,0000,0000,,He's been waiting a long\Ntime to get all ten guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.69,0:20:22.20,main,NICO,0000,0000,0000,,I think he's reckless, but I've\Nbeen watching him for four years.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.09,0:20:26.07,main,NICO,0000,0000,0000,,He always follows through \Nwhen he says he'd do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.82,0:20:30.58,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, can I make him give up?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.99,0:20:35.36,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,Can I make him give up?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.45,0:20:40.23,main,NICO,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what happened, but go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.23,0:20:41.82,main,NICO,0000,0000,0000,,It'll make things easier for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.91,0:20:45.94,main,PRINCE,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! I've still got time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.97,0:20:51.25,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, but it's better to start packing early.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.25,0:20:52.07,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.89,0:20:55.16,main,PRINCE,0000,0000,0000,,Someone help!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.16,0:20:57.89,main,PRINCE,0000,0000,0000,,It's an ogre!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.46,0:22:42.46,top,NARRATION,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: "A Single Flower."
